title: 7.2 Master Challenge 2
question:
Given below is a list of scores:
80, 83, 78, 91, 99, 67, 100, 78, 89, 92

Write a program that detects if there are any duplicate elements in this data. Print the duplicate values, if any, or a message indicating that no duplicates were found.
